@@TJvBarButtonSize
<TITLE TJvBarButtonSize type>
Summary
  The type of the ButtonSize property of TJvOutlookBar and TJvOutlookBarPage.
Description
  TJvBarButtonSize defines the allowable sizes for buttons on an OutlookBar page or on all OutlookBar pages.
  This type can have one of the following values:
@@TJvBarButtonSize.olbsLarge
  Buttons are displayed at a large size. The image (if any) is retrieved from the LargeImages
  imagelist and is displayed above the caption and the caption is centered on the button.
@@TJvBarButtonSize.olbsSmall
  Buttons are displayed at a small size. The image (if any) is retrieved from the SmallImages
  imagelist and is displayed to the left of the caption.
